results.name: Percy Jackson
results.quote: The world was collapsing, and the only thing that really mattered to me was that she was alive.

results.name: Annabeth Chase
results.quote: Even strength has to bow down to wisdom sometimes.

results.name: Jason Grace
results.quote: I'm the son of Jupiter! I'm a child of Rome, consul to demigods, praetor of the Twelfth Legion.

results.name: Piper McLean
results.quote: But what if I’m not any of the things I’ve been told I am? I have to figure out who I am.

results.name: Hazel Levesque
results.quote: I'm not choosing one of your paths. I'm making my own.

results.name: Frank Zhang
results.quote: If I'm going to burn, I might as well burn bright.

results.name: Leo Valdez
results.quote: I figure the universe is basically like a machine.

results.name: Calypso
results.quote: Love will make you do crazy things. Or, more accurately, being trapped on a deserted island for centuries will make you do crazy things.

results.name: Nico di Angelo
results.quote: Your death would be great for me.

results.name: Reyna Avila Ramírez-Arellano
results.quote: We had one home. Now we have two.

results.name: Thalia Grace
results.quote: You want some, Seaweed Brain?

results.name: Gleeson Hedge
results.quote: What about a compromise? I’ll kill them first, and if it turns out they were friendly, I’ll apologize.

results.name: Grover Underwood
results.quote: Stop it! You're as bad as Juniper. I think she wants me to run for president next.

results.name: Rachel Elizabeth Dare
results.quote: And I don't have to see the future to tell you what to do now, do I?

results.name: Tyson
results.quote: You are not dead! I like it when you are not dead!

results.name: Luke Castellan
results.quote: Ethan. Me. All the unclaimed. Don’t... Don’t let it happen again.

results.name: Clarisse La Rue
results.quote: I AM CLARISSE, DRAKON-SLAYER! I will kill you ALL! Where is Kronos? Bring him out! Is he a coward?

results.name: Bianca di Angelo
results.quote: You must listen to me. Holding a grudge is dangerous for a child of Hades. It is our fatal flaw. You have to forgive. You have to promise me this.

results.name: Will Solace
results.quote: Good. So you may be dense, but you’re not an idiot.

results.name: Charles Beckendorf
results.quote: You bet. Let's go blow Kronos back into a million pieces.

results.name: Silena Beauregard
results.quote: Charlie . . . See Charlie . . .

results.name: Stoll Brother
results.quote: Annabeth sent me a message from Tartarus. From fricking Tartarus. Anybody who can do that . . . hey, I listen to them.

results.name: Zoë Nightshade
results.quote: Stars. I can see the stars again, m'lady.

results.name: Octavian
results.quote: I am the savior of Rome! I was promised!

results.name: Poseidon
results.quote: The sea does not like to be restrained.

results.name: Athena
results.quote: I once warned you, Percy Jackson, that to save a friend you would destroy the world. Perhaps I was mistaken. You seemed to have saved both your friends and the world.

results.name: Apollo
results.quote: Always. The sun always comes back.

results.name: Ares
results.quote: That means I can smash him into a pulp as often as I want, and he'll just keep coming back for more. I like this idea.

results.name: Hephaestus
results.quote: People are more difficult to work with than machines. And when you break a person, he can’t be fixed.

results.name: Aphrodite
results.quote: To be perfect, you have to feel perfect about yourself — avoid trying to be something you're not.
